ForGG <- select(Sample2016, 3, 4, 7, 12, 14, 18:20, 26)
ggpairs(ForGG)

# Finished Sq. Feet Variable

## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'gam' and formula = 'y ~ s(x, bs = "cs")'
